text: Susan Eileen McDonald (born 7 February 1970) is an Australian politician and businesswoman. She has served as a Senator for Queensland since the 2019 federal election. She is a member of the Liberal National Party of Queensland and sits with the National Party in federal parliament. She was born in Brisbane, Queensland.
